{
  "stem": "268.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was-- and you had to perform work, mix concrete by hand, push a lorry or load up one, or unload blocks or-- one-- and then I got a job-- I used to pour concrete sections, building pillars and floor sections, as well, into forms.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so we used to lay, first, the long, long steel wires, you know, to, to make the form-- to make this-- it's called-- it's called-- in German, it's called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[GERMAN], meaning steel-- reinforced concrete.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I would-- my job was to, to put the reinforcement-- the ribs together with a-- with a-- with a pair of pliers and wires and kind of wiring it together, cross pieces, make a whole rib cage out of it-- a long one-- over which concrete would pour-- be poured, and then a section of wall would be erected, you see.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my hands were sticking to the-- to the steel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and so, so, one time I saw a guy take a cement sack and, and cleaning it out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I said, what are you doing with it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, shh.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't say that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he, and he took some-- his spoon, he had sharpened his spoon and cut a hole in it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he-- I, I, I, I watched him do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he commented to say, you know, necessity is the-- is the-- is the-- is the mother of inventions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- he-- this guy invented a vest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He must have seen it someplace else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where he got the idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I quickly-- I quickly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did-- learned from him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
